						// FEATURE: after configuring the new plot attachment,
						// immediately move the order to the plot's current
						// price + stored offset. Without this the order's
						// tracking is set up but the price doesn't update
						// until the next NinjaTrader tracking tick. Mirrors
						// the same immediate-move behavior we added to the
						// "On Off" toggle path at :34146 in
						// SetOrderIndicatorTracking, applied here so the
						// 'A' button → click plot workflow works for real
