							// cursor is currently on the line strip OR over the split
							// chip itself. Click spreads the brackets outward —
							// innermost (lowest bracket number) stays at its current
							// price, each subsequent bracket steps a configurable
							// amount further from entry. Step is computed in ticks
							// from the chart scale (~25 px per step) so it looks
